ISLAMABAD, Jan 17 (APP):The Election Commission of Pakistan (ECP) has cautioned the public to remain vigilant and disregard false information spread through a fake WhatsApp account impersonating Chief Election Commissioner (CEC) Sikandar Sultan Raja.
According to an ECP spokesperson, the recently identified fake WhatsApp account is being circulated with a picture of the CEC.
